data.description: Step into the charming 1-bedroom condo, and you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light that infuses the space with warmth and  vibrancy. The kitchen boasts a built-in breakfast bar, creating a cozy space for morning coffee or casual dining. The tiled shower is nothing  short of a masterpiece, expertly crafted to offer more than just practicality it's a true work of art. Vinings View offers an array of  exceptional amenities including pool, tennis court, fitness center, clubhouse and dog park. This condo is just minutes away from Braves  Truist Park/Battery, downtown Vinings, and more providing the best of entertainment and shopping right at your doorstep. Schedule your  showing today and make this stunning 1-bedroom condo your own slice of Vinings paradise! Easy access to I-285 and Cumberland Mall.  FHA and VA Approved
